Looking for a skilled real estate attorney to provide legal counsel on real estate transactions, contracts, and disputes. Must have experience in property law, negotiation, and litigation.

Hiring a marketing manager to develop and implement marketing strategies for real estate listings and brokerage services in the Dallas-Fort Worth area. Responsibilities include digital marketing, advertising, and branding.

Seeking a licensed real estate broker to lead a team of agents and oversee residential and commercial property transactions in the Seattle area. Must have strong leadership skills and a proven track record of sales success.

Hiring a financial analyst to provide financial analysis and modeling support for real estate investment projects in the Atlanta metropolitan area. Responsibilities include cash flow analysis, valuation, and investment performance reporting.

Looking for a skilled photographer to capture high-quality images and videos of residential and commercial properties in the Denver area. Must have experience in real estate photography and virtual tours.

Seeking an investment analyst to conduct financial analysis and due diligence for real estate investment opportunities in the Houston market. Responsibilities include market research, underwriting, and investment strategy development.
